<body>

    <h1>Welcome to Comsats University Library</h1>
    <hr>

    <p>The <b>Comsats Library</b> provides a vast collection of <i>academic resources</i>, digital journals, and a quiet environment for <u>research and study</u>.</p>

    <h2>Library Services</h2>
    <ul>
        <li>Digital Resource Center</li>
        <li>Book Lending and Reservations</li>
        <li>Research Support Services</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>Available Departments</h2>
    <ol>
        <li>Computer Science Section</li>
        <li>Management Sciences Section</li>
        <li>Electrical Engineering Section</li>
    </ol>

    <h2>Library Gallery</h2>
    <img src="https://ww3.comsats.edu.pk/isb_library/images/library_pic.jpg" alt="Comsats Library Building" width="500">
    <p><small>Figure 1: Main entrance of the library.</small></p>

    <h2>Campus Life Video</h2>
    <iframe width="560" height="315" 
        src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/dQw4w9WgXcQ" 
        title="YouTube video player" 
        frameborder="0" 
        allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture" 
        allowfullscreen>
